## 4. Code Style Guidelines

‚Ä¢ **Explicit return types** for every exported function / method.<br>
‚Ä¢ Max **3 parameters** ‚Äì otherwise use an options object.<br>
‚Ä¢ Prefer **arrow functions** for class properties.<br>
